@echo off
if "%~1"=="" (
    echo Drag a ZIP file onto this icon to convert.
    pause
    exit
)
"%~dp0zip2pdf.exe" "%~1"
pause
```

Now the user just drags their ZIP onto the `.bat` file, a console window opens showing progress, and the output ZIP appears next to the input. The `pause` at the end keeps the window open so they can read the summary.

